Marking by oceanic province

f.prod.small <- df.prod.sneha %>%
  mutate(
    Realm = case_when(
      Oceanic.region %in% c("Indian Ocean", "Asian") ~ "Indian Ocean",
      Oceanic.region %in% c("Carribbean", "n - atlantic", "s - atlantic") ~ "Atlantic",
      Oceanic.region %in% c("Red Sea", "Persian Gulf") ~ "Middle East",
      Oceanic.region %in% c("s - pacific", "spacific") ~ "South Pacific",
      Oceanic.region == "n - pacific" ~ "North Pacific",
      Oceanic.region == "Mediterranean" ~ "Mediterranean",
      TRUE ~ NA_character_
    ),
    Lat.zone = case_when(
      abs(latitude) <= 30 ~ "Tropics",
      abs(latitude) > 30 ~ "Subtropics",
      TRUE ~ NA_character_
    )
  )
